    "Note that [40] appears to be one of the most important papers as it has the highest PageRank score and it also ranks first in terms of global citations.",
    "Given that citation scores are built gradually over time, there is a lower chance of citing recent papers by highly cited papers.Table 8 Top articles based on PageRank (Author, year) Ref.",
